rComments: Best teacher ever, funny and extremely helpful

I came to the class not knowing if I would like it but this guy just makes everything fun. I really enjoyed him as a professor, he was just really awesome and funny. He's a really good teacher though and he makes learning Greek really easy.

Bossest professor I've ever had or ever will have. Really nice and funny, always likes to make jokes. Class is really laid back. You can really learn a lot in this class but it's okay if you don't, you'll still get a good grade. Really easy. Drop out of college if you get lower than an A.
